{"tid":2186950,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"今年3月31日近百名防暴闖入富健花園拘捕四名青年 一人正式被控 明天1430屯門法院提堂","createTime":"2020-09-03T10:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T04:13:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":5,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5a22f3d9f0d4a7e7eb54c3bb94f523b600e3a4a7","tid":2186950,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:14:33.000Z","msg":"李家偉 Kawai Lee &middot; 18 mins &middot; <br />\n <br />\n【331被捕者將於9月4日上庭】<br />\n<br />\n今年3月31日，首次有近百名防暴警察闖入富健花園拘捕四名青年；其中一人正式被控「在公眾地方造成阻礙」。<br />\n<br />\n手足將於9月4號（明天，周五）下晝2點半，在屯門裁判法院第1庭開庭。<br />\n<br />\n警方控罪指，事主於當日在皇珠路與其他人留下竹枝，對在上述公眾地方的人或車輛造成阻礙、不便或危險，故違反《簡易程序治罪條例》，最高刑罰為罰款$5,000或監禁3個月。<br />\n<br />\n區議會曾就此事作討論，並通過動議，要求警方詳細交代於屯門的濫權行為，特別是331及430牽涉富健花園及龍逸邨的事件。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/kawaileeFS/photos/a.113616003321378/326839035332406/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FkawaileeFS%2Fphotos%2Fa.113616003321378%2F326839035332406%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=DfqNtxIahorWM%2FuK5ta3hR9HEPLFM%2Fpg3GuXTgQF%2FE0%3D&h=b8231e55\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/kawaileeFS/photos/a.113616003321378/326839035332406/?type=3&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"0a5e9cdcf54bd2bb36ce4ec06e63d11f405d9322","tid":2186950,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"06bca652b5671d50988011f73d9b5e2d34f79d80","tid":2186950,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a5e9cdcf54bd2bb36ce4ec06e63d11f405d9322","tid":2186950,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:14:59.000Z","msg":"push"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ki